data.description: Move in ready Lennar resale in the beautiful community of Ten Trails! This high-end home is sure to impress! Located  on a dead end street, and next to a greenbelt, enjoy your privacy! 10-foot ceilings, spacious open kitchen floor plan, double oven, walk-in pantry, white quartz counters, A/C, EV charger hookup, and a covered back patio are a huge plus. Backyard has upgraded artificial grass for easy maintenance and front yard features an irrigation sprinkler system. This community is filled with parks, trails, and more!
